# Group TapUser
### 一覧 [GET /users]
ユーザーの一覧を表示する。

::: note
## Note
使い所ありませんデバッグ用です。
:::

+ Response 200
    + Body
        ```
        {
            "status": "200",
            "message": "Success! users#index",
            "data": "IIKANNZI_NI_KAETTE_KURUYO"
        }
        ```
+ Response 500
    + Body
        ```
        {
            "status": "500",
            "message": "Internal Server Error",
            "data": "(error message)"
        }
        ```
        
        
### 登録 [POST /users]
新規ユーザを登録する

+ Request (application/json)
	+ Body
        ```
        {
            "uid": "KOKO_NI_UID_WO_IRERU_YO",
            "message": "Success! users#create",
            "data": "No contents"
        }
        ```

+ Response 200
    + Body
        ```
        {
            "status": "200",
            "message": "Success! users#create",
            "data": "No contents"
        }
        ```
        
+ Response 500
    + Body
        ```
        {
            "status": "500",
            "message": "Internal Server Error",
            "data": "(error message)"
        }
        ```


