+ Response 200
    + Body
        ```
        {
            "status": "200",
            "message": "Success! users#delete",
            "data": "No contents"
        }
        ```
        
+ Response 500
    + Body
        ```
        {
            "status": "500",
            "message": "Internal Server Error",
            "data": "(error message)"
        }
        ```


# Group TapToken
トークンに関するリソーす

### 一覧 [GET /tokens/{num}]
トークンの一覧を取得する。URL内の `{num}` で指定した量だけ直近のトークンを取得することも可能。

+ Parameters
    + num: `5` (optional, int) - 取得トークン量

+ Response 200
    + Body
        ```
        {
            "status": "200",
            "message": "Success! tokens#index",
            "data": "IIKANNZI_NI_KAETTE_KURUYO"
        }
        ```
+ Response 500
    + Body
        ```
        {
            "status": "500",
            "message": "Internal Server Error",
            "data": "(error message)"
        }
        ```

### 発行 [POST /tokens]
トークンを発行する。

+ Request (application/json)
	+ Body
        ```
        {
            "uid": "KOKO_NI_UID_WO_IRERU_YO"
        }
        ```

+ Response 200
    + Body
        ```
        {
            "status": "200",
            "message": "Success! tokens#create",
            "data": {
            	"token_id": "TOKEN_NO_ID_GA_KAETTE_KURU_YO"
            }
        }
        ```
        
+ Response 500
    + Body
        ```
        {
            "status": "500",
            "message": "Internal Server Error",
            "data": "(error message)"
        }
        ```

### 移転 [PUT /tokens]
トークンを移転する。

+ Request (application/json)
	+ Body
        ```
        {
            "sender_uid": "KOKO_NI_UID_WO_IRERU_YO",
            "receive_uid": "KOKO_NI_UID_WO_IRERU_YO",
            "token_id": "KOKO_HA_TOKEN_ID_GA_HAIRU_YO"
        }
        ```

+ Response 200
    + Body
        ```
        {
            "status": "200",
            "message": "Success! tokens#update",
            "data": {
            	"token_id": "TOKEN_NO_ID_GA_KAETTE_KURU_YO",
            	"txid": "KOKO_NI_TRANSACTION_ID_GA_HAIRU_YO"
            }
        }
        ```
        
+ Response 500
    + Body
        ```
        {
            "status": "500",
            "message": "Internal Server Error",
            "data": "(error message)"
        }
        ```

### 焼却 [DELETE /tokens{token_id}]
トークンを焼却する。

+ Parameters
    + token_id: `9ao4s2L120RiGkKwJEKojL5uw7H1` (required, string) - Token's id

+ Response 200
    + Body
        ```
        {
            "status": "200",
            "message": "Success! users#delete",
            "data": {
            	"token_id": "TOKEN_NO_ID_GA_KAETTE_KURU_YO",
            	"txid": "KOKO_NI_TRANSACTION_ID_GA_HAIRU_YO"
            }
        }
        ```
        
+ Response 500
    + Body
        ```
        {
            "status": "500",
            "message": "Internal Server Error",
            "data": "(error message)"
        }
        ```